engineering concepts in a way that makes you more valuable in your current job  to future employers  and to the world at large Knowledge and skills for your next step up Knowledge and skills for your next step up Students come to the UIC online Master of Engineering program with different goals in mind  Some have their sights set on a promotion at work  Others seek a career change Graduates of the Master of Engineering online program are now working at Exelon  Graco  Johnson   Johnson  Motorola  Northrop Grumman  the University of Chicago  Advocate Good Samaritan Hospital  UI Health  and many more Several others are now PhD candidates in engineering right here at UIC Attend class from anywhere The online Master of Engineering program is set up so that all you need to attend class is a computer and an Internet connection  Classes are    % online Master of Engineering courses make learning effective and efficient campus Master of Science programs in engineering  which are conducted on campus  traveling In the last five years  UIC online Master of Engineering students have represented    U S  states and seven countries Earn your Master of Engineering degree online  Attending class is as easy as logging on from wherever you would like your classroom to be  n      APPLY NOW n      n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  nCollege of nEngineering n Footer links UIC College of Engineering UIC Makerspace Engineering Graduate Studies College Research Contact               or       meng uic edu Social Media Accounts  nFacebook n Facebook  nTwitter n Twitter  nInstagram n Instagram  nYouTube n YouTube UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 